Package: metabarcodedb
Title: Creates and Updates a Reference Database for Use with dada2
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Pip", "Griffin", email = "pip.griffin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains functions to obtain DNA sequences, ID mapping
    information and taxonomic classification for a vector of input taxonomic names.
    It allows to format the DNA sequences into the required format for use in the
    dada2 metabarcoding package.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
Imports:
    taxize,
    rentrez,
    bold (>= 0.5.0),
    stringr,
    ape,
    XML,
    dplyr,
    pbapply
Suggests: testthat
License: GPL3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
